</h1>
<div class="l-columns l-columns--66-33-large u-margin--top-none">
<div class="l-columns__column" id="main" role="main">
<p class="u-margin--top-none a-heading a-heading--3 a-heading--light">Our Life Insurance Plan pays out a lump sum if you pass away or you’re diagnosed with a terminal illness, and we’re proud that we paid out 98.6% of life claims in 2019. We’ve got different types of cover, so you can find the right option for you.
