<h2 class="a-heading a-heading--2 a-heading--semibold u-margin--top-none">Critical illness cover</h2>
</div>
<hr class="a-keyline-divider--horizontal-solid"/>
<div class="m-form-row l-max l-max--left l-max--9-column-large">
<p class="u-margin--top-none">Critical illness cover pays out a lump sum if you’re diagnosed with a life-changing illness. It’s designed to help ease any immediate financial worries you might have, and can pay towards treatment or the cost of everyday living.
		</p>
<p class="u-margin--bottom-none">We cover <a class="a-link-icon a-link-icon--download" href="https://www.aviva.co.uk/life/critical-illness-cover/policy-conditions.html" onmousedown="$p.ui.page.setShowNavigationWarning(false);" target="_blank"><span class="a-link-icon__inner">53 conditions</span></a> , including nearly all cancers, heart attacks and strokes.
		</p>
</div>
